## ⚙️ Installation & Setup

### 1️⃣ Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/taskmanage.git
2️⃣ Frontend Setup
cd task
npm run dev
App runs on:

http://localhost:5173
3️⃣ Backend Setup
cd task
cd backend
node server.js
4️⃣ Environment Variables
Create a .env file inside backend/

Example:

PORT=5000
DB_HOST=localhost
DB_USER=root
DB_PASSWORD=yourpassword
DB_NAME=taskdb
JWT_SECRET=your_secret_key
🌿 Branching Strategy
We follow a simple Git workflow:

main → Production-ready code

develop → Active development

feature/ → New features

Example:

feature/login-page
feature/task-api
feature/sidebar-ui


Commit changes:

git add .
git commit -m "Update Commit"
git push